{"word":"H4634 - מַעֲרָכָה - maʻărâkâh - mah-ar-aw-kaw' - Army","slug":"H4634","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַעֲרָכָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maʻărâkâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mah-ar-aw-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Army"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E2;&#x05E8;&#x05DB;&#x05D4; - ma&#x201B;a&#x0306;ra&#x0302;ka&#x0302;h</b> - <i>mah-ar-aw-kaw'</i><p/>Feminine of <a href=\"#/H4633\">H4633</a>; an <i>arrangement</i>; concretely a <i>pile</i>; specifically a military <i>array: - </i>army, fight, be set in order, ordered place, rank, row."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4630\">H4630</a>, <a href=\"#/H4633\">H4633</a>, <a href=\"#/H4635\">H4635</a>, <a href=\"#/H6186\">H6186</a>, <a href=\"#/H6187\">H6187</a>"}]}